data.description: Proudly presenting this lovely home in a growing area that's close to military bases, and only 10 minutes from downtown New Braunfels. Affordable, comfortable living in a home that features generous living spaces with 4 well-appointed bedrooms, ensuring everyone has their own retreat. The private backyard enjoys a covered patio that offers space to take it easy in the shade or do some grilling. The heart of this home is the open-concept kitchen fully equipped with a double oven making cooking those large meals a breeze as well as a large island where family can gather. An exciting perk is the high quality water softener and reverse osmosis system that conveys with the home! Come on over and check out this well maintained home that is turn-key, allowing you to start creating lasting memories from day one.
